{
  "texts": [
    "Post-hoc Explainable Fed-XAI: MLP-NN ConfigurationThe MLP-NN consists of two hidden layers with 128 neurons, each with the ReLu activation function.",
    "The Mean Squared Error (MSE) is adopted as loss function and Adam as optimizer.",
    "The minibatch size is set to 64.",
    "The overall number of epochs is set to 100 in the CL and LL settings.",
    "In the FL setting, we set the number of local epochs and the number of rounds as 5 and 20, respectively."
  ]
}